{"tid":2421523,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"JJ粉絲你們真的了解林俊杰嗎？知道為什麼叫他JJ嗎？","createTime":"2021-02-24T14:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T18:18:14.000Z","uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a6483f3e3201e3de84f8e3617bf627fae9ffe289","tid":2421523,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=2tnb8fs/ctp-vzntr/15236206471708sq62popop.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D2tnb8fs%2Fctp-vzntr%2F15236206471708sq62popop.jpg&h=2ca95a27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你們知道林俊傑為什麼被叫做JJ嗎？<br />\n<br />\nJJ是林俊傑的名字的簡寫，林俊傑出生在新加坡，他的英文名字是：Josephson Junction Lam，簡稱JJL，所以把林俊傑叫作JJ。要清楚一點，把林俊傑叫為JJ並不是因為林俊傑名字的拼音是JJ，因為林俊傑出生在新加坡，是新加坡人，並不是使用漢語拼音的，所以拼音名是錯誤的，這只是來源於他的外文名，即Josephson Junction Lam，簡稱JJL。"},{"pid":"87a842526d66d4c819b461d725ad479ab67bae31","tid":2421523,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8RSHwuy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8RSHwuy.jpg&h=9e378ef6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86c2c0f532c7c3c77f305a013c71aa3a959a52d7","tid":2421523,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:20:58.000Z","msg":"Jlam屈好多"},{"pid":"f4cfee3cf1f6aa841ba4afa4bcaaba7df870956c","tid":2421523,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86c2c0f532c7c3c77f305a013c71aa3a959a52d7","tid":2421523,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:20:58.000Z","msg":"Jlam屈好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:21:54.000Z","msg":"比連大哥bam咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65065194b46c175ac7d38e47c64b2f29d53974e","tid":2421523,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:25:35.000Z","msg":"JJ 賈正D"},{"pid":"b3df3a264cfb926f6f09cf1371d305f56f187974",